 arch/x86/crypto/crct10dif-pcl-asm_64.S  | 332 ------------------------
 arch/x86/crypto/crct10dif-pclmul_glue.c | 143 ----------
 arch/x86/lib/Makefile                   |   3 +
 arch/x86/lib/crc-t10dif-glue.c          |  51 ++++
